House Resolution 284
By: Representatives Martin of the 49th, Powell of the 33rd, and Frye of the 122nd
A RESOLUTION
1 Congratulating and commending Mr. Nicholas Rucker; and for other purposes.
2 WHEREAS, Mr. Nicholas Rucker is the state recipient of the Technical College System of
3 Georgia's (TCSG) 2024 Georgia Occupational Award of Leadership (GOAL), which is the
4 first program of its type in the nation to honor outstanding technical college students; and
5 WHEREAS, GOAL brings together Georgia's business, government, and industry leaders
6 with the state's technical colleges to celebrate technical education's vital impact on Georgia's
7 workforce, prosperity, and future; and
8 WHEREAS, for 52 years, the GOAL program has served as an excellent example of a true
9 partnership among business, industry, and higher education; and
10 WHEREAS, Mr. Rucker was selected from among 22 TCSG college GOAL winners who
11 have demonstrated excellent academic and leadership abilities at their respective technical
12 colleges; and
